                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-516" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN EDWARDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an upholsterer, and live in Bedford-place, Com<lb></lb>mercial-road. On the evening of the 31st of October I left my shop in the care of my shop-boy, about half-past five o'clock—I had a mahogany liquor-case on a table, nearly two yards inside the shop—this is it.</p>
